Course objectives: 
 

 To estimate index properties of soils (coarse and fine)  
 To estimate consistency limit of fine grained soils 
 To estimate shear strength of soils by direct shear test, triaxial shear test, vane shear test 

& unconfined compressive test 

 10 
 



Department of Civil Engineering, National Institute of Technology, Tiruchirappalli – 620 015. 
 

 To estimate the engineering properties of the soils by density test, CBR test permeability 
test and consolidation test 

 
