1. Grain Size analysis   
2. Consistency limits  
3. Specific gravity   
4. Permeability tests 
5. Unconfined compression test   
6. Direct shear test 
7. Core cutter and sand replacement    
8. Compaction test 
9. California bearing ratio test                         
10. Vane shear test   
11. Triaxial test   
12. Consolidation test 
 
Course outcomes: 
 
On completion of the course, the students will be able to: 
 

 classify soil by physical observation of the soils  
