CE457 STRUCTURAL DYNAMICS  
 
Course Objectives: 
 

 To introduce the concepts of dynamic systems  
 To study the dynamic response of SDOF  
 To study the dynamic response of MDOF 
 To introduce the continuous systems subjected to different types of dynamic loads 
 To learn free and forced vibrations response of structural systems 

 
Course Content 
 
